==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Cannabidaceae
<hw>Cannabidaceae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a grouping of
plants containing two genera of erect or twining wind-pollinated herbs,
the genera <gen>Cannabis</gen> and <gen>Humulus</gen>; this term is not
used in all classifications; in some the genus <gen>Cannabis</gen> is
placed in the family <fam>Moraceae</fam> and the genus
<gen>Humulus</gen> in the family <fam>Urticaceae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Cannabidaceae</fam>, hemp
family.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Cannabin</ent>⟦br⟧
